# Admin User Creation Rule

Admin must create/invite users through a production user lifecycle flow.

Required fields:
- email
- display name
- account type
- UI language
- explanation language
- timezone
- creation mode
- invitation/email verification options
- account status
- plan
- roles
- audit reason

Learner-only fields:
- target BJT level
- daily study minutes
- learning purpose
- learning personality
- furigana mode
- low-pressure mode

Forbidden:
- password input
- password_hash
- manual UUID
- manual keycloak_id
- orphan profile-only user without invitation/auth sync status
- creating admin user without RBAC/audit reason